# Directly add single file completion snippets to zinit, without the need for a plugin repository. This is useful for small snippets that don't require a full plugin structure.
# https://github.com/zdharma-continuum/zinit?tab=readme-ov-file#use-zi-ice-ascompletion-to-directly-add-single-file-completion-snippets
zinit ice as"completion"
zinit snippet https://github.com/jarun/buku/blob/master/auto-completion/zsh/_buku
